		<div class="content-center">
			<div class="row row-grid justify-content-between align-items-center text-left">
				<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6">
					<h1 class="text-white">While it's hot!</h1>
					<p class="text-white mb-3">Established in 1940, Pezza has been a small family run restaurant for many generations. In 2020, they decided to expand and open more branches, to share their amazing family secret pizza's with more people.</p>
					<div class="btn-wrapper mb-3">
						<p class="category text-primary d-inline">best italian pizza's</p>
